#
# 2. OpenAI API Key (Optional):
#    - Go to https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#    - Create a new secret key
#    - Copy and paste it as OPENAI_API_KEY
#
# 3. Google Calendar (Optional):
#    - Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
